description: The file defines the Pictogram class, which models a visual item or story consisting of multiple visual blocks. It includes metadata such as title, description, ownerId, asset URLs, and timestamp fields. The class is annotated for use with Spring Data MongoDB.

classes.name: Pictogram
classes.description: Represents a visual item or story made of multiple visual blocks, stored in a MongoDB collection with indexing constraints.
